[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    29[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Twenty MEDIUM items repeat from the chapter pattern or are recipe-new. Most are explicitly TODO'd in the recipe's prose. Six LOW items are individually minor and collectively cosmetic.
