[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    31[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Voice is excellent. **Em dash count: 0** (verified via grep for the `—` character against the published draft). The 70/30 vendor balance is maintained: AWS service names appear first in the AWS Implementation section. CC voice is consistent throughout: the Devon-at-2:14-AM opening grounds the engineer-explaining-something-cool register exactly. Self-deprecating expertise lands well throughout the Honest Take. Healthcare-domain accuracy is broadly consistent (HIPAA references correct; Schmitt-Thompson, Manchester Triage System, Emergency Severity Index references operationally accurate; HEART, Wells, Centor, Ottawa, PERC clinical-decision-rule references operationally accurate; cauda equina syndrome description operationally adequate; 988 Suicide and Crisis Lifeline reference correct; Poison Control 1-800-222-1222 reference correct; intussusception as pediatric emergency correct; FDA CDS 2022 final guidance reference operationally accurate; FDA SaMD framework reference correct; aspirin-for-suspected-MI guidance operationally accurate at 162-325 mg with appropriate TODO hedge; mandatory-reporting-laws-vary-by-state framing operationally accurate). Architectural accuracy is high. The ten-stage decomposition is the architecturally-correct shape. The Bedrock-Agents-for-tool-orchestration framing, the Bedrock-Knowledge-Bases-for-protocol-RAG framing, the OpenSearch-Serverless-for-vector-and-lexical-retrieval framing, the optional-HealthLake-for-FHIR-native-chart-context framing, the customer-managed-KMS-keys-per-data-class with separate buckets for protocol-corpus and audit-archive and triage-decision-record-journal, the Object-Lock-in-compliance-mode for the audit archive and triage-decision-record journal, and the deterministic-clinical-decision-rule-tool framing are all operationally accurate.
