[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    510[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The opening Devon-with-the-2:14-AM-chest-pressure vignette earns its position as the chapter's strongest single articulation of the patient-decision-making-under-ambiguous-acute-symptom-uncertainty failure mode.** The fortyseven-year-old, the borderline cholesterol, the father with the heart attack at 58, the eleven-minute hold time on the nurse line, the four-minute structured-triage interview, the ambulance arrival in fifteen minutes, the cath-lab placement at 4:47 AM, and the discharge on Thursday afternoon are operationally accurate and recipe-distinct.
