[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    515[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The Technology section's "Why a Generic LLM Cannot Run a Triage Bot" subsection's nine-property enumeration is recipe-distinct** and earns its position as the recipe's clearest articulation of the why-naked-LLM-in-front-of-triage-conversation-is-not-a-triage-bot primitive.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    516[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "What the Triage Bot Has To Do That the Previous Bots Did Not" subsection's six-property enumeration** is the recipe's clearest articulation of the triage-bot-vs-other-chapter-11-bots-distinction primitive. The validated-clinical-protocol-corpus-with-medical-director-sign-off, conservative-by-default-acuity-logic, continuous-emergency-screening-across-every-turn, clinical-decision-rule-computation-as-deterministic-tool, nurse-line-escalation-as-architectural-primitive, and FDA-strategy-alignment-from-day-one enumeration is operationally accurate and recipe-distinct.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    517[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "Triage Reality" subsection's twelve-property enumeration earns its position** as the recipe's most-distinctive contribution. The cost-of-being-wrong-is-asymmetric-and-severe observation, the multilingual-by-necessity observation, the accessibility-considerations-are-triage-specific observation, the mandatory-reporting-laws observation, the pediatric-and-geriatric-edge-cases observation, the social-context-the-bot-may-not-see observation, the telehealth-and-care-navigation-integration observation, the existing-care-plan observation, the telehealth-bidirectional observation, the outcome-correlation-as-long-term-commitment observation, and the liability-and-consent observation are each the recipe's right register.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    518[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "Where the Field Has Moved" subsection's ten-update enumeration earns its position.** The Schmitt-Thompson framing, the Manchester Triage System framing, the Emergency Severity Index framing, the clinical-decision-rules framing, the FDA-2022-CDS-guidance framing, the tool-using-LLMs-handle-triage-Q&A-well framing, the conversational-triage-measurably-reduces-nurse-line-wait-times framing, the equity-and-disparities-active-research-area framing, and the build-vs-buy-mature-in-this-category framing are operationally accurate and recipe-distinct.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    519[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Self-deprecating expertise lands well throughout the Honest Take.** The "the triage bot is the recipe in this chapter where the clinical stakes are highest, the regulatory exposure is most concentrated, and the accuracy floor matters most" framing is the recipe's clearest articulation of the patient-safety-acute-clinical-software primitive.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    520[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The Honest Take's ten-trap enumeration is well-chosen.** The first trap (institutional-content-as-someone-else's-problem with the multi-quarter-formalization framing), the second trap (conservative-bias-discipline with the LLM-default-helpfulness-instinct-can-erode-it framing), the third trap (regulatory-positioning with the FDA-experienced-regulatory-counsel-from-architectural-design framing), the fourth trap (citation-grounding-discipline with the bot-that-produces-ungrounded-recommendations-is-worse-than-no-triage-bot framing), and the fifth trap (continuous-emergency-screening with the patient-who-three-turns-in-discloses-cauda-equina framing) are the recipe's strongest single traps.
