[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    636[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Recipe 11.6 is publishable at the medium-complex tier level once the three HIGH findings are closed and the HEART-score sample audit-record accuracy issue (Finding A12) is resolved. The Honest Take is the recipe's strongest single passage and the chapter's strongest single articulation of the clinical-and-regulatory-engineering-outweighs-the-ML-engineering primitive in patient-safety-acute clinical software context. The "Build the institutional muscles for the harder parts first; the bot is the easier part" framing matches the chapter pattern from 11.1, 11.2, 11.3, 11.4, and 11.5 while elevating the recipe-distinct triage-bot contributions.
