[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    638[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The recipe-specific contributions that should be elevated to the chapter preface as load-bearing primitives are: (a) the **clinical-protocol-corpus-with-medical-director-sign-off-as-launch-gate primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing for any patient-safety-acute clinical-AI recipe; the corpus is the bot's clinical-safety ceiling); (b) the **conservative-bias-default-as-documented-and-audited-commitment primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; the policy is enforced architecturally, not as an emergent property of LLM helpfulness); (c) the **continuous-emergency-screening-on-every-utterance-not-just-first primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; mid-conversation emergency disclosures must trigger immediate routing regardless of where the conversation was in the protocol flow); (d) the **clinical-decision-rule-computation-as-deterministic-tool primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; the rule arithmetic is structured and the LLM does it poorly); (e) the **citation-grounding-as-launch-gate-not-post-launch-dashboard primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; ungrounded recommendations are worse than no triage bot); (f) the **FDA-SaMD-strategy-artifact-as-versioned-regulatory-asset primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; patient-facing triage tools sit on or close to the SaMD line); (g) the **nurse-line-escalation-as-first-class-capability-with-full-conversation-context-handoff primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; a bot deployed without a nurse-line backstop is missing the safety net); (h) the **per-cohort-over-triage-and-under-triage-as-separate-thresholds primitive** (recipe-distinct, patient-safety-acute; aggregate accuracy is not a sufficient metric); (i) the **outcome-correlation-pipeline-as-long-term-commitment primitive** (recipe-distinct; the bot's clinical performance is bounded above by what can be measured); (j) the **mandatory-reporting-routing-as-versioned-per-state-asset primitive** (recipe-distinct; some triage conversations surface disclosures triggering statutory reporting obligations); (k) the **pediatric-and-adult-protocol-variants-with-special-population-overlays primitive** (recipe-distinct; the protocol corpus includes both pediatric and adult variants with overlays for pregnancy, oncology treatment, transplant, geriatric); (l) the **multilingual-deployment-with-validated-translations-as-launch-day-requirement primitive** (recipe-distinct; multilingual deployment is not a phase-2 enhancement); (m) the **narrow-start-with-low-stakes-protocols-before-expanding-to-high-stakes-protocols primitive** (recipe-distinct deployment-strategy primitive; validates architecture against lower-acuity presentations before launching with high-stakes protocols); (n) the **Devon-as-canonical-user-and-canonical-cardiac-emergency-scenario primitive** (recipe-distinct; the canonical case grounds the recipe's moral case for the project); (o) the **clinical-and-regulatory-engineering-outweighs-the-ML-engineering primitive** (recipe-distinct; the operational, clinical, and regulatory engineering most clearly outweighs the ML engineering; build the institutional muscles for the harder parts first).
